    {
      "id": "PopularPost47135",
      "post_content": "This card isnt the best card, but its a fun card in a casual deck or a big multiplayer game. A fun strategy to use this card in a casual deck is to use mana ramp spells to lay out your lands fast, then you can use cards like [entomb](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=entomb) to put [realm razer](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=realm razer) into your graveyard. You then tap all you lands to float your mana, play a spell similar to [reanimate](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=reanimate) targeting realm razer, then with your remaining mana cast this enchantment and then you can choose to use realm razer as a beat stick or sacrifice foder to get your lands back thus by pass this cards weak point. not the best mana accelerant but a fun combo card",
      "posted_by": "ArturoB616",
